    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/95347142faf7dfc4cb6d3947ab004520.poster.avif?t=1768068120\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/95347142faf7dfc4cb6d3947ab004520.webm?t=1768068120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/95347142faf7dfc4cb6d3947ab004520.mp4?t=1768068120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一个充满魅力的冒险，探索一个如画般的微缩世界。探索地牢，获取强大的物品，并挑战强大的首领！但为什么呢？这个充满奇幻色彩的世界并不如它看起来那么简单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/3323ae0ac9820fb3b6eb9be855a763c8.avif?t=1768068120\" width=616 height=67 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个充满活力且风格化的世界，从西部的宏伟港口城市到东部的危险沙漠，再到北部的雪山和南部的茂密森林。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入四座神殿以及其间的多个地牢，解决谜题，获取强大的物品，并击败首领。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/2e1d8f02cadeca32ceb9265283e039f3.avif?t=1768068120\" width=1170 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 拯救世界，避免一场灾难性事件！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乘坐一辆时尚的火车环游世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据自己的喜好定制角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/5d3de324231a0f3641d29c39ae24b943.poster.avif?t=1768068120\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/5d3de324231a0f3641d29c39ae24b943.webm?t=1768068120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/5d3de324231a0f3641d29c39ae24b943.mp4?t=1768068120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整的昼夜循环和多样的动态天气！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/fd62d41dc3ed56d4965c85995f456d82.poster.avif?t=1768068120\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/fd62d41dc3ed56d4965c85995f456d82.webm?t=1768068120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219390/extras/fd62d41dc3ed56d4965c85995f456d82.mp4?t=1768068120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>这是 Steam 商店页面的初版。随着开发的推进，它将不断更新！</i></p>",
